headline: CrowdStrike Falcon Platform Achieves C5 Compliance in Germany, Strengthening Public Sector Security
summary: AUSTIN, Texas & FRANKFURT AM MAIN, Germany, December 10, 2024--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced a key government certification, achieving C5 compliance in Germany. The C5 (Cloud Computing Compliance Criteria Catalogue) certification, established by the German Federal Office for Information Security (BSI), ensures that cloud service providers meet rigorous security criteria required by public sector organizations to remain secure while delivering critical services.
